---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="AI Solutions for Battle Creek Industries | AutiMind" 
  description="Discover how AutiMind's AI solutions are transforming Battle Creek's key industries: Manufacturing, Healthcare, Food & Beverage, Automotive, Energy, and Defense. Custom AI development for Cereal City's industrial leaders."
  keywords="Battle Creek AI solutions, Michigan manufacturing AI, automotive AI development, food beverage AI, healthcare AI Battle Creek, Fort Custer AI, Denso AI solutions, Kellogg AI technology, Battle Creek industrial AI, manufacturing automation AI, cereal industry AI, automotive parts AI, defense contractor AI, energy sector AI, Michigan AI development"
  canonicalUrl="https://autimind.com/industries"
>
  <Header />
  
  <main class="pt-24">
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="py-20 px-4">
      <div class="container mx-auto max-w-6xl text-center">
        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-bold mb-8">
          <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-teal-400 to-orange-400 bg-clip-text text-transparent">
            AI Solutions for
          </span>
          <br />
          <span class="text-white">Battle Creek Industries</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-gray-300 mb-12 max-w-4xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
          Empowering Cereal City's industrial leaders with cutting-edge AI technology. From automotive manufacturing to food processing, we deliver custom AI solutions that drive efficiency, innovation, and growth in Battle Creek's diverse economy.
        </p>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8 mt-16">
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-teal-400">13,000+</div>
            <div class="text-gray-400">Fort Custer Jobs</div>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-orange-400">90+</div>
            <div class="text-gray-400">Industrial Businesses</div>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-teal-400">26</div>
            <div class="text-gray-400">International Companies</div>
          </div>
          <div class="text-center">
            <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-orange-400">$293M</div>
            <div class="text-gray-400">Recent Investment</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Manufacturing & Automotive -->
    <section class="py-20 px-4 bg-gray-800/30">
      <div class="container mx-auto max-w-6xl">
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6">
              <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-teal-400 to-cyan-400 bg-clip-text text-transparent">
                Manufacturing & Automotive
              </span>
            </h2>
            <p class="text-gray-300 text-lg mb-8">
              Battle Creek's largest employment sector with over 5,000 workers, led by Denso Manufacturing Michigan Inc. and supporting all major automakers. Our AI solutions optimize production lines, predict maintenance needs, and enhance quality control.
            </p>
            <div class="space-y-4">
              <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-teal-400 rounded-full mt-2"></div>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="font-semibold text-white">Predictive Maintenance AI</h3>
                  <p class="text-gray-400">Reduce downtime and maintenance costs with AI-powered equipment monitoring</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-cyan-400 rounded-full mt-2"></div>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="font-semibold text-white">Quality Control Automation</h3>
                  <p class="text-gray-400">Computer vision systems for real-time defect detection and quality assurance</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-teal-400 rounded-full mt-2"></div>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="font-semibold text-white">Supply Chain Optimization</h3>
                  <p class="text-gray-400">AI-driven logistics and inventory management for just-in-time manufacturing</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="relative">
            <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-teal-500/20 to-cyan-500/20 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-teal-500/30">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Key Clients</h3>
              <div class="space-y-3">
                <div class="text-gray-300">• Denso Manufacturing Michigan Inc.</div>
                <div class="text-gray-300">• Fort Custer Industrial Park Companies</div>
                <div class="text-gray-300">• Automotive Parts Suppliers</div>
                <div class="text-gray-300">• Manufacturing Equipment Companies</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Food & Beverage -->
    <section class="py-20 px-4">
      <div class="container mx-auto max-w-6xl">
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
          <div class="relative order-2 md:order-1">
            <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-orange-500/20 to-red-500/20 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-orange-500/30">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Cereal City Heritage</h3>
              <div class="space-y-3">
                <div class="text-gray-300">• WK Kellogg Co. (750+ employees)</div>
                <div class="text-gray-300">• Post Consumer Brands</div>
                <div class="text-gray-300">• Food Processing Companies</div>
                <div class="text-gray-300">• Beverage Manufacturing</div>
              </div>
              <div class="mt-6 p-4 bg-orange-500/10 rounded-lg border border-orange-500/20">
                <p class="text-sm text-orange-200">117 years of food innovation in Battle Creek</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="order-1 md:order-2">
            <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6">
              <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-orange-400 to-red-400 bg-clip-text text-transparent">
                Food & Beverage Industry
              </span>
            </h2>
            <p class="text-gray-300 text-lg mb-8">
              Building on Battle Creek's legendary cereal heritage, we provide AI solutions that modernize food production, enhance quality control, and optimize supply chains for the next generation of food manufacturing.
            </p>
            <div class="space-y-4">
              <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-orange-400 rounded-full mt-2"></div>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="font-semibold text-white">Recipe Optimization AI</h3>
                  <p class="text-gray-400">AI-powered formulation and nutrition optimization for new products</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-red-400 rounded-full mt-2"></div>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="font-semibold text-white">Food Safety Monitoring</h3>
                  <p class="text-gray-400">Real-time contamination detection and compliance automation</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-orange-400 rounded-full mt-2"></div>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="font-semibold text-white">Production Line Intelligence</h3>
                  <p class="text-gray-400">AI-driven efficiency improvements and waste reduction</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Healthcare & Social Assistance -->
    <section class="py-20 px-4 bg-gray-800/30">
      <div class="container mx-auto max-w-6xl">
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6">
              <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-green-400 to-teal-400 bg-clip-text text-transparent">
                Healthcare & Social Services
              </span>
            </h2>
            <p class="text-gray-300 text-lg mb-8">
              With over 4,000 healthcare workers in Battle Creek, we're enhancing patient care through AI-powered diagnostics, workflow optimization, and predictive analytics for better health outcomes.
            </p>
            <div class="space-y-4">
              <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-green-400 rounded-full mt-2"></div>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="font-semibold text-white">Clinical Decision Support</h3>
                  <p class="text-gray-400">AI-assisted diagnosis and treatment recommendation systems</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-teal-400 rounded-full mt-2"></div>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="font-semibold text-white">Patient Flow Optimization</h3>
                  <p class="text-gray-400">Intelligent scheduling and resource allocation for hospitals</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-green-400 rounded-full mt-2"></div>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="font-semibold text-white">Medical Imaging AI</h3>
                  <p class="text-gray-400">Advanced computer vision for radiology and pathology analysis</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="relative">
            <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-green-500/20 to-teal-500/20 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-green-500/30">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Healthcare Impact</h3>
              <div class="space-y-3">
                <div class="text-gray-300">• 4,078 Healthcare Workers</div>
                <div class="text-gray-300">• Battle Creek VA Medical Center</div>
                <div class="text-gray-300">• Bronson Battle Creek Hospital</div>
                <div class="text-gray-300">• Community Mental Health</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Energy & Defense -->
    <section class="py-20 px-4">
      <div class="container mx-auto max-w-6xl">
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
          <div class="relative order-2 md:order-1">
            <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-500/20 to-blue-500/20 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-purple-500/30">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Strategic Sectors</h3>
              <div class="space-y-3">
                <div class="text-gray-300">• Energy Infrastructure</div>
                <div class="text-gray-300">• Defense Contractors</div>
                <div class="text-gray-300">• Aviation Companies</div>
                <div class="text-gray-300">• Electric Vehicle Battery (Ford BlueOval)</div>
              </div>
              <div class="mt-6 p-4 bg-purple-500/10 rounded-lg border border-purple-500/20">
                <p class="text-sm text-purple-200">Supporting Battle Creek's strategic growth sectors</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="order-1 md:order-2">
            <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6">
              <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-400 to-blue-400 bg-clip-text text-transparent">
                Energy & Defense
              </span>
            </h2>
            <p class="text-gray-300 text-lg mb-8">
              Supporting Battle Creek's growth in energy and defense sectors with AI solutions for smart grid management, predictive maintenance, and advanced analytics for critical infrastructure.
            </p>
            <div class="space-y-4">
              <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-purple-400 rounded-full mt-2"></div>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="font-semibold text-white">Smart Grid AI</h3>
                  <p class="text-gray-400">Intelligent energy distribution and demand forecasting</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-blue-400 rounded-full mt-2"></div>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="font-semibold text-white">Defense Analytics</h3>
                  <p class="text-gray-400">Advanced data analysis and pattern recognition for defense applications</p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                <div class="w-2 h-2 bg-purple-400 rounded-full mt-2"></div>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="font-semibold text-white">Infrastructure Monitoring</h3>
                  <p class="text-gray-400">AI-powered monitoring and maintenance of critical systems</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Economic Impact -->
    <section class="py-20 px-4 bg-gray-800/50">
      <div class="container mx-auto max-w-6xl text-center">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">
          <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-teal-400 to-orange-400 bg-clip-text text-transparent">
            Driving Battle Creek's Economic Future
          </span>
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-gray-300 mb-12 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
          AutiMind is committed to supporting Battle Creek's continued economic growth and industrial innovation through AI technology that creates jobs, attracts investment, and positions Cereal City as a leader in intelligent manufacturing.
        </p>
        
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-16">
          <div class="bg-gray-800/80 p-6 rounded-xl border border-gray-700">
            <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-teal-400 mb-2">23.4k</div>
            <div class="text-white font-semibold mb-2">Total Employment</div>
            <div class="text-gray-400 text-sm">0.498% growth rate in 2023</div>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-gray-800/80 p-6 rounded-xl border border-gray-700">
            <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-orange-400 mb-2">906</div>
            <div class="text-white font-semibold mb-2">New Jobs Created</div>
            <div class="text-gray-400 text-sm">Paying $17+ per hour</div>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-gray-800/80 p-6 rounded-xl border border-gray-700">
            <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-teal-400 mb-2">21</div>
            <div class="text-white font-semibold mb-2">New Companies</div>
            <div class="text-gray-400 text-sm">Established operations in Battle Creek</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-teal-500/20 to-orange-500/20 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-teal-500/30">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Ready to Transform Your Industry?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-300 mb-6">
            Join Battle Creek's industrial leaders who are already leveraging AI to drive innovation, efficiency, and growth.
          </p>
          <a href="#contact" class="inline-flex items-center px-8 py-3 bg-gradient-to-r from-teal-500 to-orange-500 text-white font-semibold rounded-full hover:from-teal-600 hover:to-orange-600 transition-all duration-300 transform hover:scale-105">
            Get Started Today
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>